[[萬神殿|萬神殿]]皇陵儀仗隊屬於{{tsl|it|Istituto nazionale per la guardia d'onore alle reali tombe del Pantheon|萬神殿皇家陵墓儀仗隊國家學會}}，<ref>[https://www.nytimes.com/2014/08/12/world/europe/standing-guard-over-a-monarchys-tainted-legacy.html Standing Guard Over a Monarchy's Tainted Legacy] {{Wayback|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2014/08/12/world/europe/standing-guard-over-a-monarchys-tainted-legacy.html |date=20210804110506 }}. The New York Times. 11 August 2014.</ref> 以及守護{{tsl|it|Sacrario militare di Redipuglia|雷迪普利亞戰爭紀念碑}}的{{tsl|it|Guardia d'onore a Maria Santissima Regina della Pace|和平女王儀仗隊}}，是民間組織的儀仗-{}-隊伍。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://umanitadentrolaguerra.it/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/REDIPUGLIA%20-%20REGINA%20PACIS%203%20maggio%202017%20RESOCONTO%208.RI.pdf |title=Redipuglia 3 maggio 2017 |access-date=2021-06-28 |archive-date=2021-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210628112250/http://umanitadentrolaguerra.it/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/REDIPUGLIA%20-%20REGINA%20PACIS%203%20maggio%202017%20RESOCONTO%208.RI.pdf }}</ref>

